name: Kid Cudi x Been
description: This picture was taken by one of the photographers from Been corp. We had the pleasure to have kid cudi in our photoshoot. This is one of the pictures we took. You can have a poster size of it for only $5.00 signed by the man himself.

name: Heart Hat
description: The "heart" hat is a hat to match the heartbreaker tee. This comes in black and a red. The hat is great to wear and can match anything you would like to wear. This hat will become an instant classic because of its simplicity. Hurry fast, they are almost out of stock!

name: The Heartbreaker Tee (gray)
description: This product is 100% cotton. Comes is Gray and Black. The heartbreaker tee features a girl and two guys, one guy is heartbroken because the girl is falling in love with another guy. This t-shirt can relate to anyone who has had their heart broken. The text says "Heart Breaker" which shows the persona of the girl. The hearts and text are in a bright red to make them stand out. This tee is great to wear at parties and has a nice design.
